title: Additional theorems for double restricted existential uniqueness

blocks.name: 2reu8i
blocks.content: Implication of a double restricted existential uniqueness in terms of restricted existential quantification and restricted universal quantification, see also ~ 2reu8 . The involved wffs depend on the setvar variables as follows: ph(x,y), ta(v,y), ch(x,w), th(v,w), et(x,b), ps(a,b), ze(a,w) (Contributed by AV, 1-Apr-2023.)
